  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921360/extras/cd1190d43f73f56b2eb6a41a3d6df01a.avif?t=1767541304\" width=599 height=201 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Mare is a unique fast-paced gripping survival horror game that mixes classic ghost story with a nerve-wracking survival horror experience. Prey that you will survive the evil forces that lurks in the shadows of this grand mansion. Move carefully, and hide when you can. Run as fast as you can, but for all the world don't get caught.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921360/extras/2383d1c8d4b445541f83d0cc39a026d9.poster.avif?t=1767541304\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921360/extras/2383d1c8d4b445541f83d0cc39a026d9.webm?t=1767541304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921360/extras/2383d1c8d4b445541f83d0cc39a026d9.mp4?t=1767541304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a young boy trapped in an old mansion. In the game you can navigate through many of the rooms and corridors in the house, while trying to find clues and objects that are needed for the story to progress.  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921360/extras/1504184d6fa08fe81e84642d785f8bf2.webp?t=1767541304\" width=600 height=30 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921360/extras/26fd19e01f5368a8f533f31865cfb413.poster.avif?t=1767541304\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921360/extras/26fd19e01f5368a8f533f31865cfb413.webm?t=1767541304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921360/extras/26fd19e01f5368a8f533f31865cfb413.mp4?t=1767541304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use stealth to avoid drawing attention from enemies. If necessary, hide under tables, beds or inside wardrobes. You can even use an old radio receiver that reveals the enemy's location.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Psychological Survival Horror:</strong> You are not a hero, your only chance of surviving the nightmarish world of Jonah is to run, hide, and stay one step ahead of the darkness.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive Atmosphere:</strong> Stunning, high-quality visuals create a hauntingly detailed world that pulls you into the unsettling story of Jonah.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stealth and Strategy:</strong> Navigate the environment carefully with stealth-based mechanics, using the shadows and your wits to avoid the unknown.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Terrifying Unpredictability:</strong> Nothing is certain, enemies lurk where you least expect, keeping you on edge with every step.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dark Inspiration:</strong> The setting and events of Jonah draw from chilling real-world myths and psychological horror, delivering a truly disturbing experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921360/extras/ba7c179a5522d258be9837461e41fd6f.webp?t=1767541304\" width=600 height=30 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921360/extras/2244b8be8fc658c6db01a7552d6bf7c4.poster.avif?t=1767541304\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921360/extras/2244b8be8fc658c6db01a7552d6bf7c4.webm?t=1767541304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921360/extras/2244b8be8fc658c6db01a7552d6bf7c4.mp4?t=1767541304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The house is full of dark rooms and corridors that must be explored for the story to progresses. To gain access to the various rooms, you must first find the keys that fit the specific doors.  </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921360/extras/cd1190d43f73f56b2eb6a41a3d6df01a.avif?t=1767541304\" width=599 height=201 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Mare is a unique fast-paced gripping survival horror game that mixes classic ghost story with a nerve-wracking survival horror experience. Prey that you will survive the evil forces that lurks in the shadows of this grand mansion. Move carefully, and hide when you can. Run as fast as you can, but for all the world don't get caught.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921360/extras/2383d1c8d4b445541f83d0cc39a026d9.poster.avif?t=1767541304\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921360/extras/2383d1c8d4b445541f83d0cc39a026d9.webm?t=1767541304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921360/extras/2383d1c8d4b445541f83d0cc39a026d9.mp4?t=1767541304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a young boy trapped in an old mansion. In the game you can navigate through many of the rooms and corridors in the house, while trying to find clues and objects that are needed for the story to progress.  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921360/extras/1504184d6fa08fe81e84642d785f8bf2.webp?t=1767541304\" width=600 height=30 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921360/extras/26fd19e01f5368a8f533f31865cfb413.poster.avif?t=1767541304\" width=600