ted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921360/extras/2244b8be8fc658c6db01a7552d6bf7c4.poster.avif?t=1767541304\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921360/extras/2244b8be8fc658c6db01a7552d6bf7c4.webm?t=1767541304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921360/extras/2244b8be8fc658c6db01a7552d6bf7c4.mp4?t=1767541304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The house is full of dark rooms and corridors that must be explored for the story to progresses. To gain access to the various rooms, you must first find the keys that fit the specific doors.  </p>",
